  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2944936/" class="title-link">“六股文书评”</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2944936"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/lvchashuqing/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1053455-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lvchashuqing/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">绿茶</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-01-20"
      class="main-meta">2010-01-20 17:01:19</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2944936_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      “六股文”是老六独创的碎片式文体，控“六”的老六，在涉及到数字时均喜欢以“六”代之。想当年，他主持文青腐败论坛“饭局通知”时，“六股文”盛行，最常见为“关于今晚饭局的六件事”、“关于今晚牌局的六件事”或“关于周日山局的六件事”等等，这些碎片化的细节记录...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2944936/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">9有用 / 5没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2944936_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2944936_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
